cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with automatic segmentation of liver lesions using deep learning methods, specifically fully convolutional networks (FCNs) and deep residual networks (ResNet). This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of ResNet also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves medical imaging (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with the segmentation of liver lesions in medical images.
